    {
      "id": "el_7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 100,
      "width": 337,
      "height": 22,
      "text": "Mean Price Formula",
      "fontSize": 17,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 17,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 700,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 7,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f1"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Mean Price Formula",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 125,
      "width": 297,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "Mean = (C×Qc + D×Qd) / (Qc + Qd)\n\nMean price always lies BETWEEN\nthe cheaper and dearer prices\n\nWeighted average of all components\n\nWHY: Total cost / total quantity gives\nthe average price per unit.\n\nEx: 5kg at Rs.20 + 3kg at Rs.30\n  Mean = (100+90)/8 = Rs.23.75/kg",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 800,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 8,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f1"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Mean = (C×Qc + D×Qd) / (Qc + Qd)\n\nMean price always lies BETWEEN\nthe cheaper and dearer prices\n\nWeighted average of all components\n\nWHY: Total cost / total quantity gives\nthe average price per unit.\n\nEx: 5kg at Rs.20 + 3kg at Rs.30\n  Mean = (100+90)/8 = Rs.23.75/kg",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
