    {
      "id": "el_45",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1253,
      "width": 303,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Op 1: 60x4/5 = 48L\nStep 2: Op 2: 48x4/5 = 38.4L\nStep 3: Op 3: 38.4x4/5 = 30.72L\n\n  60 ─×4/5─→ 48 ─×4/5─→ 38.4 ─×4/5─→ 30.72\n  Survival fraction = (60-12)/60 = 4/5\n\nTRICK:\nFormula: V x (1-x/V)^n\n= 60 x (1-12/60)^3\n= 60 x (4/5)^3 = 60 x 64/125\n= 30.72L (51.2% left)\n\nAnswer: 30.72 litres ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 4500,
