      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1601,
      "width": 830,
      "height": 33,
      "text": "Three types of rice at Rs 20, Rs 25, and Rs 30 per kg are\nmixed in ratio 2:3:5. Find the cost of the mixture per kg.",
