    {
      "id": "el_60",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1666,
      "width": 339,
      "height": 245,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Total cost:\n  20x2+25x3+30x5 = 40+75+150 = 265\nStep 2: Total qty = 2+3+5 = 10 kg\nStep 3: Mean = 265/10 = Rs 26.50/kg\n\n  [2kg @20] + [3kg @25] + [5kg @30] = [10kg @?]\n  Cost = 40 + 75 + 150 = 265\n  Mean = 265/10 = 26.50\n\nTRICK:\nWeighted avg formula:\n= (CxQ sum) / (Q sum)\n= 265/10 = 26.50\nCloser to 30 (largest qty) ✓\n\nAnswer: Rs 26.50/kg ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 6000,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 60,
