      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_9"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Total cost:\n  20x2+25x3+30x5 = 40+75+150 = 265\nStep 2: Total qty = 2+3+5 = 10 kg\nStep 3: Mean = 265/10 = Rs 26.50/kg\n\n  [2kg @20] + [3kg @25] + [5kg @30] = [10kg @?]\n  Cost = 40 + 75 + 150 = 265\n  Mean = 265/10 = 26.50\n\nTRICK:\nWeighted avg formula:\n= (CxQ sum) / (Q sum)\n= 265/10 = 26.50\nCloser to 30 (largest qty) ✓\n\nAnswer: Rs 26.50/kg ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
