      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Milk fractions:\n  C1=3/5, C2=5/8, Target=7/11\nStep 2: Let ratio = x:y\n  (3x/5+5y/8)/(x+y) = 7/11\n  Cross multiply and solve:\n  x:y = 16:5\n\nTRICK:\nAlligation on milk fractions:\n  3/5       5/8\n    \\       /\n     7/11\n    /       \\\n  (D-M)   (M-C)\n= (5/8-7/11):(7/11-3/5)\n= 16:5\n\nAnswer: Ratio = 16:5 ✓",
